<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title><%= content_for?(:title) ? yield(:title) : "Boson Foundry" %></title>

    <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application" %>
    <%= javascript_include_tag "vendor/modernizr" %>
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="top-bar">
      <ul class="title-area">
        <li class="name">
        <h1><%= link_to "Boson Foundry", root_path %></a></h1>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <section class="top-bar-section">
      <ul class="right">
        <li class="divider"></li>
        <% if user_signed_in? %>
          <li> Signed in as <%= current_user.email %> Not you? <%= link_to 'sign out', destroy_user_session_path, method: :delete %></li>
        <% else %>
        <li class="divider"></li>
          <%= link_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path %> or <%= link_to 'sign in', new_user_session_path  %> </li> 
        <li class="divider"></li>
        <% end %>
        <li><%= link_to "Posts", posts_path %></li>
        <li class="divider"></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Prodjects List", projects_path%></li>
        <li class="divider"></li>
        <li><%= link_to "Contact Us" %></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="flash">
      <p class="notice"><%= notice %></p>
      <p class="alert"><%= alert %></p>
    </div>
    <div class="large-8 columns"><%= yield %></div>
    <div class="large-4 columns">
      <div class="about-us">
        <h2>
          About Us
        </h2>
        <p>
        I am a Ruby on Rails software developer who lives in the Pacific Northwest. Writing good software
        that is clean, flexible, documented, and fast is a passion which I enjoy. Creating a UI that is easy
        to navigate, draws a customer to a CTA or inspires a user to investigate further brings an immense degree
        of satisfaction in my work. Creativity, clear communication, and working with others to make something
        great is the most satifying thing in my life.

        </p> 
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= javascript_include_tag "application" %>
</body>
</html>
